<item>
            <title>[LU-19137] Support for kernel 6.15</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19137</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Update support for kernel 6.15:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;wait_on_page_locked() removed&lt;br/&gt;
    open code the folio compat wrapper until general folio support is landed.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;grab_cache_page_write_begin() removed&lt;br/&gt;
    open code the folio compat wrapper until general folio support is landed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hrtimer_init removed &amp;#8211; use hrtimer_setup() and provide compat for older kernels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;sysctl_vfs_cache_pressure removed, use vfs_pressure_ratio() compat for el7?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;inode_operations-&amp;gt;mkdir() should return a dentry() compat for older kernels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
